@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<!-- About-Section -->
<section id="about" class="about-section bg-secondary-subtle py-5">
    <div class="container rounded">
        <h1 class="mb-4 fw-bold">FitSphere Fitness</h1>
        <p class="text-black fw-medium">
            At FitSphere Fitness, we are dedicated to helping you achieve your health and fitness goals.
            Our state-of-the-art facilities, passionate trainers, and supportive community make us the
            perfect partner in your fitness journey. Whether you’re just starting or looking to reach
            new levels, we’ve got you covered.

            <br><br>

            We believe in a holistic approach to fitness that includes physical strength, mental resilience,
            and a healthy lifestyle. Our diverse programs cater to all fitness levels, from beginner
            workout sessions to advanced training for seasoned athletes. Each class is carefully designed
            to keep you motivated and challenged, so you’ll never feel like your fitness routine is stagnant.

            <br><br>

            Our team of certified trainers has extensive experience in various disciplines, including
            weight training, cardio fitness, yoga, and wellness coaching. They are not just experts in their
            field but are also genuinely passionate about helping you unlock your full potential. You can
            expect personalized guidance and tailored programs that align with your fitness goals.

            <br><br>

            At FitSphere, we also value community. Our members are part of a supportive and encouraging
            network that fosters growth, teamwork, and friendship. Whether you're working out solo or attending
            one of our group fitness classes, you’ll feel the energy and camaraderie that makes us different from
            any other gym.

            <br><br>

            We're here to empower you—no matter your age, background, or fitness level. Join us today
            and experience the FitSphere difference. Together, we'll work towards a healthier, stronger,
            and more confident version of you.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

